title: Dui Prithibi
subTitle: Raised by his widowed mother, Tonmoy is a collegian in love with Moina. He loses his memory after a violent altercation and is taken to his father's friend's house where he falls in love with Farah.

title: Bikram Singha: The Lion Is Back
subTitle: Gupi, an imposter, finds a gang of thugs pursuing him after a six-year-old girl believes him to be her father. Later, he learns a shocking secret about the girl's life.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: As the gods seek Parvati's blessings before their fight, Tarakasura tries to take advantage of Shiva's absence to cause chaos amongst them.

title: Pujarini
subTitle: Arindam and Pujo marry each other secretly as her mother is against their alliance. Later, circumstances force them to live separately but Arindam pledges to unite with his love.

title: Shatruta
subTitle: Avijit and Avinash are partners but the latter frames Avijit for killing their manager and acquires the entire business. Avijit's son, Bijoy, decides to take revenge on Avinash.

title: Sedin Dekha Hoyechilo
subTitle: Kavita's father holds his daughter's lover's friends captive and asks them to reveal the couple's whereabouts. However, one of the boys, Abir, falls in love with his other daughter, Nandini.

title: Nawab Nandini
subTitle: Nabab and Nandini, once childhood sweethearts, meet again in college and fall in love despite their differences.

title: Kartabya
subTitle: A bridegroom disagrees to marry due to the non-payment of dowry by the bride's father. In spite of his brother's request, he remains stubborn and decides to stop his wedding.

title: Kencho Khunrte Keute
subTitle: Gyanoda loses his son and daughter-in-law, leaving his granddaughter Parama as a spoilt child. To discipline her, he leaves a will which requires her to marry to gain full inheritance access.

title: Kencho Khunrte Keute
subTitle: Gyanoda loses his son and daughter-in-law, leaving his granddaughter Parama as a spoilt child. To discipline her, he leaves a will which requires her to marry to gain full inheritance access.

title: Durga Sohay
subTitle: A mother-daughter relationship develops between Manasi, the younger daughter-in-law of an aristocratic family, and Durga, a maid, when she gives her a second chance after the house-help is caught stealing.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Tarakasura believes that Parvati will respond to the gods' pleas. He then decides to take advantage of the time during incarnation to kill her.

title: Madhur Milan
subTitle: Sunita, who hails from a rich family, is mesmerised by Gopal's music. Their interactions over time compel them to believe they are lovers from a previous life.

title: Criminal
subTitle: Shiba, an orphan turned criminal, decides to mend his ways after falling in love with a woman named Sanchari. However, circumstances force him to re-enter the world of crime.

title: Khoka 420
subTitle: Krish is the son of a rich man and is in love with Megha. However, things become complicated when Megha's best friend, Bhoomi, enters their lives and falls in love with Krish.

title: Chirodini Tumi Je Amar
subTitle: Pallavi, a rich, spoilt girl, falls in love with Krishna, a scooter mechanic, and gets married without her parents' approval. The situation takes an ugly turn when her family tries to separate them.

title: Yuddha
subTitle: Agnishwar Rai, a noble officer, is stone-hearted towards criminals and gets arrested when he puts an MLA behind bars. Filled with anger, he avenges his wife's death, after she was murdered by the same bureaucrat.

title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

title: Bindaas
subTitle: Abhi falls in love with Kajol and convinces her family to get them married. However, things get complicated when Kajol's uncle asks him to kill their rival's son, who is none other than Abhi himself.

title: Jeevan Yodhha
subTitle: After a lot of trials and tribulations, Avinash manages to build a business empire. However, when his sister's corrupt husband kills her, he sets out to seek revenge.

title: Shiv Shakti
subTitle: Diti requests that Tarkasura get rid of Parvati instead of randomly targeting baby girls. The gods are delighted by the news of Shakti's rebirth as Parvati.

title: Byabodhan
subTitle: Though Bhaskar loves Mitra, he marries Sushmita, a poor woman, at his father's behest. Even after the wedding, Bhaskar refuses to accept his wife plunging her into despair.

title: Bidhatar Khela
subTitle: Biswanath's wife, Uma, accepts and loves his family members like her own. However, things change when his brother marries a rich girl and their family gets separated.

title: Villain
subTitle: Riya meets Sneha on a flight back home and they strike up a conversation. Surprisingly, Sneha's fiance turns out to be a lookalike of Riya's boyfriend, leaving her in a state of shock.

title: MLA Phatakesto
subTitle: A notorious goon aspires to become a member of the Legislative Assembly and in an attempt to do so, he gives himself seven days.

title: Bhalobasa Bhalobasa
subTitle: Sidhu meets and falls in love with a woman named Priya despite being engaged to a different girl. He soon has to make a choice between following his heart and respecting his father's wishes.

title: Chhoto Bou
subTitle: A mother-in-law treats her daughters-in-law, Mamta, Tandra and Deepa, according to their husband's income. However, when she falls ill, she realises her folly.

title: Love Marriage
subTitle: A young couple brings their families to get to know each other. However, the two are shocked when they realise their parents used to date.
